{"id":275382,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/01/维权网-北京德赛电脑培训班如期开课（图）/","date":"2013-01-20T10:30:45Z","modified":"2013-01-20T10:30:45Z","title":"维权网 | 北京德赛电脑培训班如期开课（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员唐韵报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日</span><span>星期六，在北京主要为上访维权人士授课的德赛电脑培训班如期开课。虽然学习班的横幅不见了，但前来参加这期学习班的人较前两次多了。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">60</span><span>名学员把教室挤得满满的，有的学员只好站在外面听课。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>元月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">14</span><span>、</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15</span><span>日被抓走（除 胡俊雄 老师外）的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>名学员也都来到学习班，学员们互相问候，并向他们表示致意！大家一个共同的心愿：学好电脑，回报老师，回报社会。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>中午开饭时，志愿者王福全讲述了 胡梭雄 老师买了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>斤腊八米，准备熬腊八粥与大家共度腊八，因学习班遭到警方干扰，未能如愿。全体学员报以掌声对 胡 老师表示敬意！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>参与电脑培训学习班打扫卫生、买饭、送饭的志愿者有：段淑兰、贾凤琴、王福全、王心灵、罗志淑等人。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-OhQCKvqsR-E/UPuysg6Xe7I/AAAAAAAAZkE/hccDo0HX_v8/s1600/%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-OhQCKvqsR-E/UPuysg6Xe7I/AAAAAAAAZkE/hccDo0HX_v8/s320/%E7%94%B5%E8%84%91.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"s